  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK741">
<l>āṟṟu pavarkku maraṇporu ḷañcittaṟ</l>
<l>pōṟṟu pavarkkum poruḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A fort is an object of importance to those who march (against their foes) as well as to those who through fear (of pursuers) would seek it for shelter.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
